# Instant Pot Beef Stew

Based on [The Kitchn](http://web.archive.org/web/20251021094246/https://www.thekitchn.com/instant-pot-beef-stew-22949287) ([wayback](http://web.archive.org/web/20251021094246/https://www.thekitchn.com/instant-pot-beef-stew-22949287))

